spec_data.Name: dustin-dustismo-fonts-common
spec_data.Description:
General purpose fonts by Dustin Norlander available in
serif and sans-serif versions. The fonts cover all European Latin characters.

This package consists of files used by other dustin-dustismo-fonts packages.
